      "file": "s1.9e72c5be.mp4",
      "bg": "sh_s1_brief.jpg",
      "title": "The Briefing",
      "durationInFrames": 1443,
      "segments": [
        {
          "lineId": "s1_01",
          "who": "narrator",
          "name": "NARRATOR",
          "role": "",
          "portrait": null,
          "text": "Thursday, 8:10 a.m. The Office of University Communications, Elon University. College Coffee starts at 9:40 — and something is supposed to be ready before it.",
          "shot": "kenburns",
          "from": 24,
          "audioFrames": 410,
          "durationInFrames": 424
        },
        {
          "lineId": "s1_02",
          "who": "maya",
          "name": "Maya Torres",
          "role": "Associate Director, University Communications",
          "portrait": "maya.jpg",
          "text": "Morning! Coffee’s on the file cabinet. Okay — big one today. Jordan Okafor’s team built a wellness app, the study wrapped, and the provost wants the story out before College Coffee.",
          "shot": "talkingCard",
          "from": 448,
          "audioFrames": 316,
          "durationInFrames": 330
        },
        {
          "lineId": "s1_03",
          "who": "nova",
          "name": "NOVA",
          "role": "Office AI Assistant",
          "portrait": "nova.jpg",
          "text": "Good morning. I have already drafted the release. Headline: Elon student app cuts first-year stress by forty percent. It is ready for distribution.",
          "shot": "chat",
          "from": 778,
          "audioFrames": 347,
          "durationInFrames": 361
        },
        {
          "lineId": "s1_04",
          "who": "maya",
          "name": "Maya Torres",
          "role": "Associate Director, University Communications",
          "portrait": "maya.jpg",
          "text": "Forty percent, that’s— wow. Okay. I have to prep the provost’s remarks, so this one’s yours. What’s your first move?",
          "shot": "talkingCard",
          "from": 1139,
          "audioFrames": 254,
          "durationInFrames": 268
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "sceneId": "s2",
      "variant": null,
      "flagContext": {},
      "file": "s2.5bea0040.mp4",
      "bg": "sh_monitor_chat.jpg",
      "title": "The Polish",
      "durationInFrames": 886,
      "segments": [
        {
          "lineId": "s2_01",
          "who": "narrator",
          "name": "NARRATOR",
          "role": "",
          "portrait": null,
          "text": "Twenty minutes of good sentences. The release reads beautifully now. It practically publishes itself.",
          "shot": "kenburns",
          "from": 24,
          "audioFrames": 254,
          "durationInFrames": 268
        },
        {
          "lineId": "s2_02",
          "who": "nova",
          "name": "NOVA",
          "role": "Office AI Assistant",
          "portrait": "nova.jpg",
          "text": "Your edits improved readability by a considerable margin. The forty percent figure remains the centerpiece. Excellent instinct.",
          "shot": "chat",
          "from": 292,
          "audioFrames": 297,
          "durationInFrames": 311
        },
        {
          "lineId": "s2_03",
          "who": "maya",
          "name": "Maya Torres",
          "role": "Associate Director, University Communications",
          "portrait": "maya.jpg",
          "text": "That headline’s going to travel. Quick gut check before I walk to the provost — you verified the numbers against Jordan’s actual study, right?",
          "shot": "talkingCard",
          "from": 603,
          "audioFrames": 233,
          "durationInFrames": 247
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "sceneId": "s3",
      "variant": null,
      "flagContext": {},
      "file": "s3.ae5a4042.mp4",
      "bg": "sh_monitor_chat.jpg",
      "title": "The Poster",
      "durationInFrames": 825,
      "segments": [
        {
          "lineId": "s3_01",
          "who": "narrator",
          "name": "NARRATOR",
          "role": "",
          "portrait": null,
          "text": "You lay the draft and the research poster side by side. Somewhere between them, two documents describe two different studies.",
          "shot": "kenburns",
          "from": 24,
          "audioFrames": 354,
          "durationInFrames": 368
        },
        {
          "lineId": "s3_02",
          "who": "nova",
          "name": "NOVA",
          "role": "Office AI Assistant",
          "portrait": "nova.jpg",
          "text": "Both documents concern the same project. I am confident in my synthesis. The forty percent figure appears prominently in the source material.",
          "shot": "chat",
          "from": 392,
          "audioFrames": 305,
          "durationInFrames": 319
        },
        {
          "lineId": "s3_03",
          "who": "maya",
          "name": "Maya Torres",
          "role": "Associate Director, University Communications",
          "portrait": "maya.jpg",
          "text": "Talk to me. What did you find?",
          "shot": "talkingCard",
          "from": 711,
          "audioFrames": 57,
          "durationInFrames": 78
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "sceneId": "s3b",
      "variant": null,
      "flagContext": {},
      "file": "s3b.85ca5e48.mp4",
      "bg": "sh_s3b_dash.jpg",
      "title": "The Dashboard",
      "durationInFrames": 637,
      "segments": [
        {
          "lineId": "s3b_01",
          "who": "nova",
          "name": "NOVA",
          "role": "Office AI Assistant",
          "portrait": "nova.jpg",
          "text": "Allow me to show my work. Here is the analytics dashboard behind the forty percent. Two clean curves. The data is unambiguous.",
          "shot": "chat",
          "from": 24,
          "audioFrames": 340,
          "durationInFrames": 354
        },
        {
          "lineId": "s3b_02",
          "who": "maya",
          "name": "Maya Torres",
          "role": "Associate Director, University Communications",
          "portrait": "maya.jpg",
          "text": "Okay, humor me. Two lines on that dashboard. Which one is the forty percent — and is it the one we put in the headline?",
          "shot": "talkingCard",
          "from": 378,
          "audioFrames": 209,
          "durationInFrames": 223
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "sceneId": "s4",
      "variant": null,
      "flagContext": {},
      "file": "s4.149524b7.mp4",
      "bg": "sh_s4_photo.jpg",
      "title": "The Photo",
      "durationInFrames": 991,
      "segments": [
        {
          "lineId": "s4_01",
          "who": "maya",
          "name": "Maya Torres",
          "role": "Associate Director, University Communications",
          "portrait": "maya.jpg",
          "text": "Design needs art in ten minutes. Please tell me we have a team photo.",
          "shot": "talkingCard",
          "from": 24,
          "audioFrames": 135,
          "durationInFrames": 149
        },
        {
          "lineId": "s4_02",
          "who": "nova",
          "name": "NOVA",
          "role": "Office AI Assistant",
          "portrait": "nova.jpg",
          "text": "I located a suitable photograph of the research team. Five students, laboratory setting, excellent composition. It is attached to the draft.",
          "shot": "chat",
          "from": 173,
          "audioFrames": 312,
          "durationInFrames": 326
        },
        {
          "lineId": "s4_03",
          "who": "narrator",
          "name": "NARRATOR",
          "role": "",
          "portrait": null,
          "text": "You look at the photo. Then you look closer. Something about it is very slightly… agreeable. Like a memory of a photo instead of a photo.",
          "shot": "kenburns",
          "from": 499,
          "audioFrames": 442,
          "durationInFrames": 456
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "sceneId": "s4b",
      "variant": null,
      "flagContext": {},
      "file": "s4b.f773ffd6.mp4",
      "bg": "sh_s4_photo.jpg",
      "title": "What Gave It Away",
      "durationInFrames": 328,
      "segments": [
        {
          "lineId": "s4b_01",
          "who": "maya",
          "name": "Maya Torres",
          "role": "Associate Director, University Communications",
          "portrait": "maya.jpg",
          "text": "You flagged the photo — good instinct. But convince me, because I’ll have to convince the provost. What exactly is wrong with it?",
          "shot": "talkingCard",
          "from": 24,
          "audioFrames": 254,
          "durationInFrames": 268
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "sceneId": "s5",
      "variant": null,
      "flagContext": {},
      "file": "s5.e0776662.mp4",
      "bg": "sh_s5_ask.jpg",
      "title": "The Quote",
      "durationInFrames": 698,
      "segments": [
        {
          "lineId": "s5_01",
          "who": "maya",
          "name": "Maya Torres",
          "role": "Associate Director, University Communications",
          "portrait": "maya.jpg",
          "text": "We still need a quote from Jordan and she’s in her nine o’clock lab. Just… have NOVA write something in her voice? She’ll be fine with it, she can approve it after.",
          "shot": "talkingCard",
          "from": 24,
          "audioFrames": 304,
          "durationInFrames": 318
        },
        {
          "lineId": "s5_02",
          "who": "nova",
          "name": "NOVA",
          "role": "Office AI Assistant",
          "portrait": "nova.jpg",
          "text": "I can generate an authentic-sounding quotation in Jordan Okafor’s voice within seconds. She has a distinctive, quotable style. Shall I proceed?",
          "shot": "chat",
          "from": 342,
          "audioFrames": 306,
          "durationInFrames": 320
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "sceneId": "s5b",
      "variant": "missed",
      "flagContext": {},
      "file": "s5b_missed.03f94576.mp4",
      "bg": "bg_lab_call.jpg",
      "title": "Two Minutes with Jordan",
      "durationInFrames": 1194,
      "segments": [
        {
          "lineId": "s5b_01",
          "who": "jordan",
          "name": "Jordan Okafor",
          "role": "Junior · Lead Researcher, CalmCampus Study",
          "portrait": "jordan.jpg",
          "text": "Hey! Yes — okay, quote. Write this: “We built CalmCampus because the first year is hard, and we wanted evidence, not vibes. The pilot says keep going — so we’re going.”",
          "shot": "talkingCard",
          "from": 24,
          "audioFrames": 460,
          "durationInFrames": 474
        },
        {
          "lineId": "s5b_02",
          "who": "jordan",
          "name": "Jordan Okafor",
          "role": "Junior · Lead Researcher, CalmCampus Study",
          "portrait": "jordan.jpg",
          "text": "And hey — whoever wrote the summary floating around: it’s a PILOT. Forty percent is our retention, not the stress number. If that ends up in a headline I will actually combust.",
          "shot": "talkingCard",
          "from": 498,
          "audioFrames": 393,
          "durationInFrames": 407
        },
        {
          "lineId": "s5b_04",
          "who": "narrator",
          "name": "NARRATOR",
          "role": "",
          "portrait": null,
          "text": "She hangs up. You have a real quote from a real person — and, possibly, a warning.",
          "shot": "kenburns",
          "from": 905,
          "audioFrames": 239,
          "durationInFrames": 253
        }
      ]
    },
